  <eligibility>
    <criteria>
      <textblock>
        Inclusion Criteria:

          -  Every elective midline laparotomy for patients with Abdominal Aortic Aneurysm and
             patients with a BMI of more than 27.

          -  Signed informed consent

        Exclusion Criteria:

          -  Age &lt; 18 years

          -  Emergency procedure

          -  Inclusion in other trials

          -  Aortic reconstruction for obstructive disease

          -  Life expectancy less than 24 months

          -  Pregnant women
      </textblock>
    </criteria>
